description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to analyze the Cowboys victory over the Giants on Monday Night Football (1:00). The guys discuss the black cat on the field, Daniel Jones' lack of development, Pat Shurmur's coaching cowardice, how dangerous Dallas can be moving forward and another pass interference mistake. Next, Will, Ryan, John and Sean react to a report that moving to London could be a possibility for the Chargers (32:30). They also hit on news items around the NFL (51:30) and answer 5-star reviews from Apple Podcasts (1:05:30).
